   Breast Cancer Res. 2015; 17: 39.
   Published online 2015 Mar 17. doi: 10.1186/s13058-015-0536-9
   PMCID: PMC4362830
   PMID: 25849111

Estimated dietary dioxin exposure and breast cancer risk among women from the
French E3N prospective cohort

   Aurélie MN Danjou,^1,^2 Béatrice Fervers,^ corresponding author ^1,^2
   Marie-Christine Boutron-Ruault,^3,^4,^5 Thierry Philip,^1,^2 Françoise
   Clavel-Chapelon,^3,^4,^5 and Laure Dossus^1,^3,^4

